Package Lab3.Compulsory

Class Relationship

  • java.lang.Object
    • Lab3.Compulsory.Relationship
  • public class Relationship
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing a Relationship between two Nodes in a network. This class contains a node and a context that describe the relationship. The node represents the second node from the relationship. The context represents the reason that bounds the two nodes together.
